         <abstract id="aspace_dfc84da6841284cc7201f993a636f4ab">Miscellaneous records and studies of insurance companies in Connecticut. Included is an agent's register (1870-1881), letter books of the State Fire Insurance Company (1860-1861), and a study by Richard M. G. Potter of the Aetna Life Insurance Company.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_e4d8aa4f5ea250b262c964ac715acf0f">
